To write an algorithm and flowchart to find the 2nd largest number


Algorithm:

Step 1: Declare an integer array
Step 2: Get the size of the array from user as ‘i’
Step 3: Get the inputs 
Step 4: Check if i < 2, if yes print invalid number of inputs and stop the execution
Step 5: Else sort the array in descending order
Step 6: Print the first index (i.e) second element of the array as the second largest number  
